Name: Cooling and heating circulating pump YR05001 // YR05004
Short description: Manufacturer: Kalstein\n\n
Description:
YR series cooling and heating circulating pump is the most widely used circulationg pump for chemical reactors.
Features
  • It contains refrigerating system, heating system, pre-cooling system, three systems can be used continuously and also can be used separately
  • Fast heating and cooling and temperature can be increased and lowered continuously
  • Wide temperature control range, no need of changing heat-conducting medium in the whole course and little consumtion of heat-conducting medium
  • Complete closed circulating system, the heat transfer fluid is not easy to volatilize and oxidize at high temperature, or not easy to absorb moisture under low temperature, which can prolong the service life of heat transfer fluid
  • High temperature cooling and refrigeration function, can lower from high temperature level directly
  • Refrigeration heat exchanger adopts complete brazing type, small space and high-efficiency heat exchanging

Name: Beer Refractometers YR05939 // YR05943
Short description: Manufacturer: Kalstein\n\n
Description:
The Kalstein hand-held optical refractometer measures the density of sugars in the solution and gives you an instant gravity reading at any point during the boil, or run off from the mash. You do not need to convert the reading from Brix to specific gravity or do an adjustment for temperature. Great for quick and frequent check on the gravity of your running or while sparging, and also for those who do not like to deal with the temperature compensation necessary with a hydrometer. Unlike a hydrometer, it only requires a very small amount sample, about 2-3 drops of sample only.
Features:
  • High quality body construction
  • Uses ambient light only which means battery or power source is not required
  • Easy to focus and calibrate
  • Cushioned with soft & comfortable non-slip rubber
  • With ATC function (Auto Temperature Compensation)
  • Durable and built to last long
